4 unit Belgian Waffle
1 unit French Macarons
8 ounce Lemon Cheesecake
3.5 ounce SkinnyDipped Strawberry Lemonade Almonds

Heat a waffle iron. Add waffle to iron. Warm for about 30 seconds. TOASTER OR OVEN ALTERNATIVE: Heat toaster or traditional oven to low. Add waffle to toaster or oven. Warm for about 1 minute. MICROWAVE ALTERNATIVE: Microwave waffle for 20 seconds.

Arrange macarons, waffles, cheesecakes, and SkinnyDipped Strawberry Lemonade Almonds on a board or platter and serve! (If you’re feeling fancy, arrange the desserts on a cake stand or fine china plates.)